        <div class="body">
            <p>Validation is done by Zend_File_Transfer and not by Zend_Form_Element_File.
The validation is either done by calling the isValid() method or by calling the receive() method which itself calls the isValid() method.</p>

<p>As you can see, the receive() method is called by Zend_Form_Element_File which means that file uploads are also validated.</p>

